itemDescription: English socialite; wife of British Prime Minister Harold Macmillan

wikipedia_page.main: Lady Dorothy Evelyn Macmillan  (née Cavendish; 28 July 1900 – 21 May 1966) was an English socialite and the third daughter of Victor Cavendish, 9th Duke of Devonshire, and Evelyn Cavendish, Duchess of Devonshire. She was married to Harold Macmillan from 1920 until her death.
